Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是熊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能假裝沒看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你幹嘛要過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個只有那邊的自動販賣機裡才有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真宵為什麼會穿成這樣出現在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:01:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天拿到了這個熊熊裝 所以想要嚇大家一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在遇到第一個人的時候就失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 話說這個熊熊裝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很普通地把你臉露出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.91,0:01:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算突然冒出來 我覺得也沒那麼嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬無一失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個特技挺嚇人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現第二個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摘希跟真宵約好了見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 這樣不就會被她意識到我要嚇她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摘希對這個特別敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在摘希同學一邊這樣想著 一邊在這等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊禦好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是睡過頭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天積了雪 變冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他快點來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想快點將——伊禦的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋整個咬住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先不管內容真假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後有沒有加了一個很詭異的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我差不多該上了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.09,syl2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(938,312)\c&H163F74&}襲擊開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.09,syl2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1A4076&\pos(942,672)}（第{\c&HFCFCFD&}二{\c&H153F73&}人）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:01.07,syl5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HE4917F&\pos(478,4)}（冰冷的視線）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還是放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.84,syl2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5C6866&\pos(260,684)}第二人 失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 摘希同學是為了跟伊禦同學一起去學校才等在這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你確實經常跟伊禦同學一起去學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是偶遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上遇到了 就一起與學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為遇到的地點不固定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非摘希同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天巧妙地變換地點跟時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創造不會引人懷疑的完美偶遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:04:59.03,syl2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(866,430)}那是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來小姬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不是一直都一起來學校的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了嚇她 今天我跟她約了地方碰頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連同沒有成功的摘希同學和伊禦同學的份 我要好好嚇嚇她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姬應該會被嚇到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把小姬嚇到腳軟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驚嚇太過的話 小姬會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脖子軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脖子軟了 動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脖子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.79,syl2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1A3F72&\pos(936,316)}襲擊開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.79,syl2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H183D70&\pos(942,666)}（第{\c&HBEFFFA&}三{\c&H164073&}人）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真宵同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熊用兩隻腳站著 追過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩隻腳站著…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我要的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎 小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是真的在逃命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.11,0:06:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我沒想到你會嚇成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 給你手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是遇到熊用運動員的跑步姿勢追過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般都是會嚇到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更正一下 可以說是恐怖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實很恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是榊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還要嚇榊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼簡單地突擊榊同學 能有效果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是方法不得當 說不定反而會被他看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:07:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用兩隻腳跑 還是用四隻腳跑 哪種好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不給他反應的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他一開始也會嚇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐著雪橇的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紋絲不動地 快速追過來怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去試試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ready
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.19,syl5,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H5E6A68&\pos(640,270)}空罐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是伊 伊禦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把事情原原本本地告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為是紋絲不動的熊 坐在雪橇上 快速追來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了超級衝撞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不知道自己在說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦子沒摔壞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 這不是跟你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算是成功把榊同學也給嚇著了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很不甘心 但是真的衝擊太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟都撞飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說回來 那樣都嚇不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只有美衣子姐和禦庭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…就算是美衣子姐 遇到這種情況也會嚇一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想像不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是可以微笑的場景啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 就當美衣子姐是嚇不倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方發現菊繪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是我決定進行獎勵任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:07.13,syl8,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(954,106)}獎勵任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 也算我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有你助陣真宵的預演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是一下子就看的出來是惡作劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我用手邊的東西變裝一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是員警 一定會毫不猶豫地逮捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.43,syl2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H194075&\pos(948,322)}襲擊開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.43,syl2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H163E75&\pos(942,666)}（第{\c&H1CC5F0&}五{\c&H173E72&}人）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看起來很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:01.63,syl8,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HC0726C&\pos(642,52)}捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摘希
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我故意在那兒等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們以後約一個時間地點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.52,0:10:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從明天起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 沒問題是沒問題 但是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個季節的早晨很冷 之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.67,0:10:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是的 真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快停下來啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就是寒假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 把24號空著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和小姬那天有事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什喵！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摘希同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了摘希 一臉失落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊禦同學完全沒明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姬和我還有榊都要上班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.66,0:11:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要去打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天又沒什麼要事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NOOOOOO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得的耶誕節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的事可以做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和戀人從「早上好」到「晚安」…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和戀人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相注視著對方生活之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那對情侶在耶誕節到底想幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那天還有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家一起開聖誕Party喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真宵同學非常消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有約的話也是沒辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說話方式也很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後伊禦同學和小姬就可以一起過耶誕節了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:57.17,syl7,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H894552&\3c&H252525&\frz341.498\move(190,618,226,522)}\N故\N意\N把\N話\N題\N挖\N出\N來\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是打工而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連摘希同學也這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 一起來吧 臨時打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.71,0:13:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美衣子也希望有人幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做我做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和大家一起聖誕打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你們來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就請大家多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:14:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就拜託兩位和伊禦一起在店門口銷售聖誕蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著聖誕裝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美衣子小姐 我是穿制服的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定很適合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊禦同學處於壓倒性劣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美衣子姐是伊禦少數的弱點之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.76,syl2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0D2E61&\pos(300,474)}衣服換好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好暖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕裝還真暖和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熱乎乎的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這種時期才能穿真是太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.63,0:14:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摘希同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是最小號了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛哦 摘希同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得挺合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊禦也很合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任誰看了都會被迷倒的聖誕老人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊禦聖誕老人會送怎樣令人驚喜的禮物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是心潮澎湃心跳加速的禮物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心跳加速
